  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrc="shortdesc:1;6:14" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/cascading-in-a-ditamap.dita">Certain map-level attributes cascade throughout a map, which facilitates attribute and
    metadata management. When attributes <term class="- topic/term " xtrc="term:1;7:48" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/cascading-in-a-ditamap.dita">cascade</term>, they apply to the elements that are
