      <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:2;27:10" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/cascading-in-a-ditamap.dita"><ph class="- topic/ph " xtrc="ph:2;27:15" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/cascading-in-a-ditamap.dita">Cascading is additive for attributes that accept multiple
          values, except when the <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:1;28:43" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/cascading-in-a-ditamap.dita">cascade</xmlatt> attribute is set to avoid adding values
