      <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:7;93:10" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/cascading-in-a-ditamap.dita">For map A, the values for the attribute are merged, and the effective value of the
          <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:13;94:19" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/cascading-in-a-ditamap.dita">audience</xmlatt> attribute for <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrc="filepath:1;94:61" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/cascading-in-a-ditamap.dita">topic.dita</filepath> is "a b c". For
