      <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:10;108:10" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/cascading-in-a-ditamap.dita">The reference to <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrc="filepath:4;108:37" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/cascading-in-a-ditamap.dita">two.dita</filepath> turns off merging, so the explicit
